descriptionHtml:
FEEL FREE TO CONTACT ME WITH ANY QUESTIONS OR CONCERNS!

This mod adds a Whiterun themed underground home to your Skyrim, just outside of Whiterun. It features a main gate, fortress walls, and an entrance to a large cave inside the cave home, yes I know... Caveception. Anyways, it's somewhat navmeshed since I don't understand how to use navmesh too well. Well, you've read this far, might as well download it k thx bye.

* INCLUDES *

2 Bedrooms
Armory
Bar
Cave
Kitchen
Throne
Small Island in Cave
author: Sir Ethan
